data.description: This 3 bedroom 2 bath, 2 car garage home is one of the larger 3 bedroom models, which allows for a larger living and kitchen area. Situated in a convenient location, it is within close proximity to various stores and restaurants, allowing for easy access to amenities. Additionally, being close to the interstate offers convenience for those who commute. This home features gas appliances. The stove and oven are gas, as well as the dryer and the hot water heater. The back yard is its own little oasis,and has plenty of room for activities and entertaining. Built in 2008, this house is relatively new, ensuring modern features and a sturdy structure. The neighborhood is highly sought after due to its great reputation and friendly atmosphere. There are low HOA fees and No CDD fee to help keep expenses down for homeowners. The best part about this home is the seller is offering a 1 year home warranty and the home has already had a 4 point inspection done and the report is available to see! This house offers a great combination of location, features, and a desirable community. Don't miss the chance to make it your new home.
